                        <h4><a class="text-white" href="https://test.joonaslindroos.com">Fax or Cap</a></h4>
                        <p class="desc-text">A straightforward web application enabling users to create posts, which others can then vote on as either true or false. The user interface is minimal, as the primary objective of the project was to gain hands-on experience with databases and SQL.</p>
                        <div class="btn-group w-100" role="group">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary tech tech-node" type="button">Node.js</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary tech tech-mysql" type="button">MySQL</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary tech tech-ejs" type="button">EJS</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary tech tech-express" type="button">Express</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col pt-3 pt-lg-5" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500" data-aos-delay="100">
