                    <div class="order-last order-lg-first py-4 py-lg-0 px-lg-4">
                        <h4><a class="text-white" href="/snake/pvp">Two Player Snake</a></h4>
                        <p class="desc-text">An enhanced version of the classic Snake game designed for two players, where the goal is to outmaneuver and cause the opponent to crash. The game supports both local multiplayer on the same device and online multiplayer through WebSocket communication.</p>
                        <div class="btn-group w-100" role="group">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary tech tech-node" type="button">Node.js</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary tech tech-websockets" type="button">Websockets</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary tech tech-express" type="button">Express</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-100">
                        <a href="/snake/pvp">
                            <img class="rounded img-fluid d-block w-100 fit-cover" style="height: 200px;" src="/res/images/PvPSnakeGame.png" alt="Two Player Snake image">
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col pt-3 pt-lg-5" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="500" data-aos-delay="100">
