                    </div>
                    <div class="py-4 py-lg-0 px-lg-4">
                        <h4><a class="text-white" href="/snake/comp">One Player Snake</a></h4>
                        <p class="desc-text">A straightforward implementation of the Snake game, designed to deepen familiarity with backend technologies while incorporating enhanced graphics for an improved gameplay experience. The application also includes a leaderboard feature to track and display top scores.</p>
